article_title: Like Senate Bill, No Obamacare In President's Immigration Order

og.description: As President Obama tonight unveils an executive order that will shield as many as five million people from deportation and enable them to get permits to work legally in the United States, they are not expected to be eligible for health coverage under the Affordable Care Act.
